    <item>
      <title>债券销售激增 债务基金经理带上笔记本电脑度假</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/debt-fund-managers-pack-laptops-for-vacation-as-bond-sales-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年夏天，企业在美国债务市场大举借贷，促使基金经理在外出度假时带上笔记本电脑，而这个时间原本是一年中的淡季。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/debt-fund-managers-pack-laptops-for-vacation-as-bond-sales-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 16:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>空客季度盈利因航天部门收费而下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/airbus-tktktkt-on-slower-plane-deliveries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[空中客车集团第二季度的营业利润下降了一半以上，原因是该公司在其航天部门登记了一笔费用，迫使其在飞机交付量低于预期的情况下削减成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/airbus-tktktkt-on-slower-plane-deliveries</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:52:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>监狱电话公司 ViaPath 在新的 FCC 规则下完成 13.8 亿美元债务出售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/prison-phone-company-viapath-wraps-up-1-4-billion-debt-sale-after-new-fcc-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国联邦通信委员会出台新规定限制监狱通信提供商 ViaPath Technologies 的通话收费标准，该公司暂停了该流程，目前已完成 13.8 亿美元的再融资交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/prison-phone-company-viapath-wraps-up-1-4-billion-debt-sale-after-new-fcc-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:49:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>穆迪将英国南部水务公司的评级下调至垃圾级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/uk-s-southern-water-risks-downgrade-to-junk-by-moody-s</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆迪评级正在考虑将英国公用事业公司南方水务公司的优先债务评级下调至垃圾级，这一最新迹象表明，泰晤士水务公司的困境可能蔓延至英国水务行业的其他领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/uk-s-southern-water-risks-downgrade-to-junk-by-moody-s</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:35:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国在工业界抗议下提高北海石油和天然气税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/uk-raises-north-sea-oil-gas-taxes-amid-protest-from-industry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国新政府履行承诺，加强对北海石油和天然气生产商的税收制度，增加暴利税并取消一些投资津贴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/uk-raises-north-sea-oil-gas-taxes-amid-protest-from-industry</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:22:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿拉比卡咖啡价格因供应担忧缓解而维持近三周低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/arabica-coffee-holds-near-three-week-low-on-easing-supply-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商评估了主要种植区巴西冬季的温和天气条件以及需求疲软的风险，阿拉比卡咖啡期货交易价格接近三周来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/arabica-coffee-holds-near-three-week-low-on-easing-supply-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 12:22:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Grifols 审计后将中国股权价值削减 4.57 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/grifols-new-auditor-finds-non-cash-accounting-discrepancy-linked-to-china-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年遭受做空者攻击的西班牙制药公司 Grifols SA 表示，它夸大了其在一家中国公司的股份价值，并报告了 4.57 亿欧元（4.94 亿美元）的会计调整。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/grifols-new-auditor-finds-non-cash-accounting-discrepancy-linked-to-china-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 11:53:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利率决定公布前，欧洲股市因稳健数据上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/european-stocks-hold-steady-on-solid-data-before-rate-decisions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[因有报告显示欧元区经济上季度增长超过预期，欧洲股市上涨，投资者关注本周美国和英国央行的利率决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/european-stocks-hold-steady-on-solid-data-before-rate-decisions</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 07:22:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储公布财报前股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大公司的抛售导致股价下跌，交易员们准备迎接科技巨头的盈利和央行的决策，这些将是影响市场走势的关键。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 22:47:22 GMT</pubDate>
